es of weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Make use of powerful support abilities. Such as artillery strikes and deployable turrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Defeat 3 different enemy sub-factions. Each with their own unique units and environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Fight across Planet-X with environments ranging from sand dunes to frozen wastelands and from forests to megacities  </p></li></ul>","developers":["Mid Development"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237920/header.jpg?t=1738185915","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257060788,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257060788/movie480.mp4?t=1728598393","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257060788/movie_max.mp4?t=1728598393"},"name":"Gameplay Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257060788/a125311d3ffa7814e1b4d982b94b21004b39e7a3/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1728598393","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257060788/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1728598393","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257060788/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1728598393"}}],"name":"Mech Havoc","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> i5-8400<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> Integrated Graphics<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 2 GB available space</li></ul>"},"platforms":{"linux":false,"mac":false,"windows":true},"publishers":["Mid Development"],"ratings":{"dejus":{"banned":"0","descriptors":"Viol\u00eancia","rating":"10","rating_generated":"1","required_age":"10","use_age_gate":"0"},"steam_germany":{